## LdmlKeyboardCompiler.loadTestData() method

Loads a LDML Keyboard test data xml file and compiles into in-memory xml structures.


|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  filename | string | input filename, will use callback to load from disk |
